data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
GroupBar provides option to show ContextMenu with the user desired functionalities.
GroupBar.ShowContextMenu event is used to show the ContextMenu.
With the use of PointToClient method, the ContextMenu is made visible on the selected GroupBarItem in runtime.

data.name: label33.Text
data.value:
Essential GroupBar provides support for huge set of events.
Other than the default events, GroupBarItemAdded GroupBarItemRemoved GroupBarItemRenamed GroupBarItemSelected GroupBarITemSelectionChanging NavigationPaneDropDownClick ProvideGroupBarItemBrush ShowContextMenu are triggered by GroupBar to make easy customization.

data.name: label24.Text
data.value: Essential GroupBar provides various advanced features such as * Hosting Custom controls * Nested groupBar support * Appearance customization * Huge set of events * Context Menu * Localization
